      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen in showroom condition. This vehicle has been maintained to the highest standards, exhibiting no discernible wear and retaining its original factory luster. Every detail, from the immaculate interior upholstery to the flawless exterior finish, confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning collector. We invite you to experience a level of automotive excellence that defines the benchmark for pre-owned luxury.",
