    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless. If you're looking for something that's basically perfect and ready for a new home, this is the one. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to believe how clean it is!",
      "price": 46500.0,
