      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! This car has been babied since day one\u2014always garage-kept and kept in truly pristine condition. It looks and drives just like it did the day I brought it home. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new and ready for the road, you\u2019ve found it! I'd love for this beauty to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
