    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen remains in a strictly stock configuration, showcasing a flawless factory finish and a pristine interior. Mechanically, the dual-VANOS system has been proactively serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides precise, tactile engagement, routing power through a healthy variable M differential lock. With a dry undercarriage, zero fluid seepage, and perfect compression across all cylinders, this M3 delivers the high-revving, linear power delivery enthusiasts crave. A turn-key collector piece for the most discerning purist.",
